replies.body:
I didn't mean to imply it was a problem as much as when making changes to a system while specifically targeting Soraka we should keep in mind there would be casualties (unintended or otherwise) in the kits of other characters.

This thread was targeted towards healing and shielding supports so I figured I should mention some characters outside that scope that this change would effect. It is best to consider all angles and potential side-effects of a big change like this, isn't it?

